content: Do the same with this next passage, "I am decent man who is honest, out-going, and absolutely self-confident. A man who loves himself foremost, his family--- One who loves ideas,traveling, the good things in life , but who will endeavor to handle the not so pleasant,concomitant aspects of life, and still smile, a man who is generous,kind and has plenty of sympathy for the less fortunate. And above all, a man who is always the peace maker in a world that is so "peace less""
